This Power BI project visualizes physiological and behavioral data collected from a smart wearable band prototype, aimed at analyzing mood patterns, stress indicators, and well-being metrics.

Developed as part of the Ideathon organized by NERDS Robotics Club, NIT Silchar, this dashboard forms the analytical front-end of the MoodSense system â€” an intelligent mood tracking solution using biosensors like GSR and HRV to monitor mental wellness in real time.

ğŸ” This dashboard displays 30 days of personal health and mood data recorded from a single individual using the smart wearable band.

